  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located around 1.5 kilometres from Byggen Wharf, the Magic Hotel Solheimsviken sits in Bergen's business district, outside of the main touristic centre.</p>
<h2>Head to the tram to reach Bergen's main centre</h2>
<p>The hotel is only a short walk from the Danmarksplass light rail station so you can hop on the tram and be in Bergen central in 20 minutes. You're also around 20 minutes by bus from the Ulriken cable car station, just walk from the bus stop to the cable car, buy your tickets and be swept up the Bergen's highest mountain. At the top enjoy panoramic views of Bergen and there's also some walking trails to explore.</p>
<h2>Eclectic décor</h2>
<p>The hotel's interiors have been designed by designer Karim Rashid - the décor is vibrant and contemporary with comfortable rooms.</p>]]></description>
